						               													<description>Play as a biathlete in an unbearable suspense race. Biathlon Crystal Globe offers you the possibility of competing in all biathlon disciplines (Sprint, Pursuit, Mass Start, Relay, etc.). One day race, season or Championship. &amp;#10;Become master of the Crystal Globe!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Choose his characteristics, rather very good at shooting or very good at skiing, unless you prefer him to be good in both disciplines. Each type of biathlete has its own movement die. Build your race to surprise your opponents. You have energy cards that allow you to make the difference in the terrible climbs to leave your competitors behind. But this reserve is not inexhaustible. It's a safe bet that the fate of your race will be decided on the shooting range.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Shooting lying down or standing up, with or without wind, you will have to choose for your biathlete between a fast but risky shot or a more steady and safer shot. Two very different strategies but both can be winning. Because each missed ball will make you lose a lot of time on the penalty ring. It's up to you to choose the one that will win the day before you make the last lap, with the other biathletes chasing you.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Goal of the game: Embody a biathlete during an unbearable suspense race.&amp;#10;How to play: Choose their characteristics, rather very good at shooting or very good at skiing, unless you prefer them to be good in both disciplines. Each type of biathlete has its own set of movement die, shooting dice and Energy deck. &amp;#10;You have energy cards that allow you to make the difference in the terrible climbs to leave your competitors behind. But this reserve is not inexhaustible. It's a safe bet that the fate of your race will be decided on the shooting range.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Shooting lying down or standing up, with or without wind, you will have to choose for your biathlete between a fast but risky shot or a more steady and safer shot. Two very different strategies but both can be winning. Because each missed ball will make you lose a lot of time on the penalty ring. It's up to you to choose the one that will win the day before you make the last lap, with the other biathletes chasing you.&amp;#10;End of the game: Cross the finish line.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash; Description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
